name: You Like Wine 1
description:
"You Like Wine 1" is a high resolution scan of a physically plotted SVG file, created by me using my own software and drawn using a robot I designed and built. The plot is coded with the date/time produced, and hand-signed.

Shipping of the original plot to the first buyer is included in the price. (Subsequent buyers must pay the seller for shipping the original.)

I create art using software I created and robots I designed and built. This physical plot is unique, and will never be recreated. 

Follow my artwork on twitter at @photopuck and mastodon at smerp@mastodon.art
